# index.html Round 2 patches

Apply this patch to your mainline aging-app/index.html to register
the new C2 stylesheet.

## Patch - Add stylesheet link

Find the existing stylesheet links in <head>. v2.2 mainline already
includes the global stylesheet (and likely v2.2 dashboard styles).

Add a new <link> for the C2 stylesheet, AFTER any existing v2.2
stylesheet links so the C2 rules can override or augment them:

```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/v2.3-aging-report.css" />
```

If your build pipeline imports CSS via JavaScript instead of HTML
<link>, instead add this import at the top of AgingReportPage.tsx:

```typescript
import '../styles/v2.3-aging-report.css';
```

Either path works. Pick the one consistent with how your mainline
loads other component stylesheets (e.g. dashboard.css, party-detail.css).

## Verification

After applying:

1. `npm.cmd run build` succeeds.
2. Dev server serves the new stylesheet without 404.
3. /aging page renders with styled callout, summary strip, tabs.
4. Round 2 invariants (inv-aging-ui-css-load) confirm the stylesheet
   path is referenced in either index.html OR AgingReportPage.tsx.
